            "image_position": "top",
            "heading": "OUR STORY (1 OF 5)",
            "text": "I'm Dominique, Mother of MANCUB. The idea was born in 2017 when I bumped into an old friend. It wasn’t her I spotted though, it was her husband & son; they were dressed head-to-toe in matching designer gear, and turned heads everywhere they walked. It’s as if they were wearing their FatherSon bond for all to see.",
