            "image_position": "center",
            "heading": "OUR STORY (2 OF 5)",
            "text": "We got talking, and I asked about the matching outfits and why they were doing it. She explained how it started as a fad when she first bought them similar looking t-shirts for their holiday, but ever since, her son has refused to leave the bedroom unless he ‘looks like daddy’.",
