            "image_position": "center",
            "heading": "OUR STORY (3 OF 5)",
            "text": "Adorable in principle, but unless you want cheap, low quality slogan t-shirts printed with ‘half pint’ & ‘full pint’, there’s not much out there. I wanted to create something for the style conscious male that takes his role as dad seriously, and wants to match whilst looking good.",
            "box_position": "left"
          }
        },
        "slide_fG6xz9": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ManCub_LaunchParty_239.jpg",
            "image_position": "center",
            "heading": "OUR STORY (4 OF 5)",
            "text": "Fast forward 17 months and MANCUB was officially launched. We celebrated with a party – an amazing event filled with Men & Cubs from all over the UK celebrating their bond whilst mums watched on with pride.",
            "box_position": "left"
          }
        },
        "slide_ECw9Rq": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/David-Willey.jpg",
            "image_position": "center",
            "heading": "OUR STORY (5 OF 5)",
            "text": "I hope you love MANCUB as much as I have loved building it. There is no better feeling than receiving photos of your amazing MANCUB moments, so keep them coming.",
